<section class="faq" aria-label="Help Center">
  <div class="faq-left">
    <h2>Help Center (FAQ)</h2>
    <p>
      Here you can find answers about contact, shipping, and returns. If you need help, write to us at
      <a class="faq-link" href="mailto:info@gethr2.com">info@gethr2.com</a>.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 16px;">
      <a class="faq-link" href="#help-center">Help Center (FAQ)</a><br>
      <a class="faq-link" href="#contact">Contact</a><br>
      <a class="faq-link" href="#shipping">Shipping &amp; Delivery</a><br>
      <a class="faq-link" href="#returns">Returns</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-right">
    <h3 id="help-center">Help Center (FAQ)</h3>

    <div class="faq-item open">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
        <span>What is the fastest way to reach support?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">â€“</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        The fastest way is by email at <a class="faq-link" href="mailto:info@gethr2.com">info@gethr2.com</a>.
        If available, include your order number so we can help you faster.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Where can I find information on ingredients and research?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        You can find ingredient details on <a class="faq-link" href="{{ pages['inhaltsstoffe'].url | default: '/pages/inhaltsstoffe' }}">Ingredients</a>
        and background on quality and evidence on <a class="faq-link" href="{{ pages['forschung'].url | default: '/pages/forschung' }}">Research</a>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 id="contact" style="margin-top: 28px;">Contact</h3>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Which contact details can I use?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Email: <a class="faq-link" href="mailto:info@gethr2.com">info@gethr2.com</a><br>
        For legal information, please also see our <a class="faq-link" href="{{ pages['impressum'].url | default: '/pages/impressum' }}">Legal Notice</a>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How quickly will I receive a response?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        We respond as quickly as possible. During peak times it can take longer. If your request concerns an order,
        your order number helps us assign it quickly.
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 id="shipping" style="margin-top: 28px;">Shipping &amp; Delivery</h3>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How long does shipping take?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Delivery time depends on destination country and shipping method. The estimated delivery time is shown at checkout
        or in your order confirmation.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How much are shipping costs?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Shipping costs vary by destination country and are displayed transparently at checkout before you complete your order.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Can I track my shipment?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Once your order has shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation with tracking information (if available).
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 id="returns" style="margin-top: 28px;">Returns</h3>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How do I start a return?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Email us at <a class="faq-link" href="mailto:info@gethr2.com">info@gethr2.com</a> with your order number and reason for return.
        We will reply with the next steps.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Is there a right of withdrawal?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        Information on withdrawal is available on our <a class="faq-link" href="{{ pages['widerruf'].url | default: '/pages/widerruf' }}">Right of Withdrawal</a> page.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>When will I receive my refund?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
        After receiving and checking your return, we refund to the original payment method. Depending on your payment provider,
        it may take a few days for the credit to appear.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
